08:45.232 --> 08:46.599
You know how
we decided on "Sing"

08:46.600 --> 08:48.067
by My Chemical Romance
for Regionals?

08:48.068 --> 08:51.070
Well, I hold in my hand a cease
and desist letter from the band.

08:51.071 --> 08:52.105
We can't do it.

08:52.106 --> 08:53.472
It was the perfect anthem.

08:53.473 --> 08:54.824
How much do you want to bet

08:54.825 --> 08:56.059
Coach Sylvester has something
to do with this?

