One step ahead of you.

08:57.411 --> 08:58.911
Do you know
anything about this, Sue?

08:58.912 --> 09:01.364
I do. Now,
I met the drummer

09:01.365 --> 09:03.649
from My Chemical Romance at a
drum circle at Daytona Beach,

09:03.650 --> 09:05.618
Spring Break, 1996.

09:05.619 --> 09:06.986
We had a brief affair.

09:06.987 --> 09:09.756
And when I heard of your
song choice for Regionals,

09:09.757 --> 09:12.491
well, I was compelled
to notify the band

09:12.492 --> 09:15.327
about your long-running
legal battle with PETA.

09:15.328 --> 09:17.213
That is not true.

09:17.214 --> 09:19.182
You took away my Cheerios!

09:19.183 --> 09:24.220
Consider this the opening
salvo of World War Sue.

09:24.221 --> 09:25.605
So what are we going to do now?

09:25.606 --> 09:28.691
I think we should write
original songs for Regionals.

09:28.692 --> 09:31.444
All those in favor of voting
Rachel down a second time?

09:31.445 --> 09:32.962
No. I think
Rachel is right.

09:32.963 --> 09:35.231
