to sing the duet with Kurt.

12:34.936 --> 12:37.538
That's ridiculous.

12:37.539 --> 12:39.323
I mean, there are
so many great voices.

12:39.324 --> 12:41.075
I mean, everyone deserves
a shot at that honor.

12:41.076 --> 12:43.744
All in favor of Kurt being my
duet partner at Regionals?

12:47.049 --> 12:48.582
Decided.

12:48.583 --> 12:49.834
Congratulations, Kurt.

12:49.835 --> 12:51.618
Congratulations.

