Tina and I have been already
working on a song that I wrote.

13:09.237 --> 13:10.971
Really?
That's amazing.

13:10.972 --> 13:12.657
Well, can we hear it?

13:17.079 --> 13:18.829
This is a song
that I wrote for Sam.

13:18.830 --> 13:19.997
It's called,
"Trouty Mouth."

